<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.254859>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. 1 — Corimalia strejceki, paratype, male, habitus, 2 — Corimalia aliena, male, habitus, 3 — Corimalia strejceki, female, habitus, 4 — Corimalia aliena, female, habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/254859/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.254860>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 12. Corimalia strejceki, paratype, male genitalia (5 – 8). 5 — penis, lateral view, 6 — penis, dorsal view, 7 — tegmen, 8 — apex of penis; Corimalia aliena, male genitalia (9 – 12). 9 — penis, lateral view, 10 — penis, dorsal view, 11 — tegmen, 12 — apex of penis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/254860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.254861>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 14. 13 — Corimalia strejceki, paratype, mucro and comb of setae on apex of metatibia in male; 14 — Corimalia aliena, mucro and comb of setae on apex of metatibia in male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/254861/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

